        <item>
            <title>1.0.22</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new</h3>
<ul>
<li>Normal Mail now requires a license. On launch, enter your license key to activate the app. You can purchase a license or manage activation from the activation screen and in Settings → License.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
